FLUX 2 Quality 1.title: FLUX 2 Quality 1
FLUX 2 Quality 1.description: This is a FLUX 2 Quality 2 tier. The difference vs Quality 1 is that, this one uses 2x faster sampler. That is why. The difference is minimal. Moreover you can increase step count to 40 for more quality.

FLUX 2 Quality 2.author: local
FLUX 2 Quality 2.title: FLUX 2 Quality 2
FLUX 2 Quality 2.description: This is a FLUX 2 Quality 2 tier. The difference vs Quality 1 is that, this one uses 2x faster sampler. That is why. The difference is minimal. Moreover you can increase step count to 40 for more quality.

FLUX Dev Models.author: local
FLUX Dev Models.title: FLUX Dev Models
FLUX Dev Models.description: FLUX Dev Models - Krea and SRPO as well: 20-40 Steps - Just change base model to FLUX Dev or FLUX Krea or FLUX SRPO. You can use GGUF models as well

FLUX Kontext Dev Edit Images.title: FLUX Kontext Dev Edit Images
FLUX Kontext Dev Edit Images.description: Official FLUX Kontext Dev Edit Any Image

Inpainting Preset.author: local
Inpainting Preset.title: Inpainting Preset
Inpainting Preset.description: Use this preset to inpaint small areas as shown in tutorial video. Just directly apply when doing inpainting. It will only change inpainting Init Image related parameters. Set step count accordingly. For example when Init Image Creativity is set to 0.6, you need 7 steps do to actually 4 steps. E.g. Qwen Fast LoRA requires 4 steps. So set steps count to 7 in this case.

Outpainting Preset FLUX Dev Fill.author: local
Outpainting Preset FLUX Dev Fill.title: Outpainting Preset FLUX Dev Fill
Outpainting Preset FLUX Dev Fill.description: This is a preset to do outpainting on images with FLUX Fill Dev model as shown in tutorial.  Currently FLUX Fill Dev model is the very best to outpaint images without changing rest of the image. Outpaint images with small portions if you get errors. Try multiple different seeds if you don't get perfect results.

Qwen Image 50 Steps Official Slow.author: local
Qwen Image 50 Steps Official Slow.title: Qwen Image 50 Steps Official Slow
Qwen Image 50 Steps Official Slow.description: This is Qwen image 50 steps official quality. Steps set to 50 but you can reduce to 20 with some quality loss. It is slow. Compare with Qwen Image 8 Steps and see if it worths it.

Qwen Image 8 Realism Fast.author: local
Qwen Image 8 Realism Fast.title: Qwen Image 8 Realism Fast
Qwen Image 8 Realism Fast.description: This is fast Qwen Image Realism generation with Qwen Image Edit Speed up LoRA (this works best for realism). Only 8 steps and CFG 1. It uses newest res_2s Sampler and beta57 Scheduler for realism. res_2s is 2x slower than euler but much better realism.

Qwen Image 8 Steps Ultra Fast.author: local
Qwen Image 8 Steps Ultra Fast.title: Qwen Image 8 Steps Ultra Fast
Qwen Image 8 Steps Ultra Fast.description: This is ultra fast Qwen Image generation with official latest lightx2v LoRA. Only 8 steps and CFG 1 therefore it is 12 times faster than official workflow. Its quality almost matching the official workflow.

Qwen Image Edit Plus 12 Steps.author: local
Qwen Image Edit Plus 12 Steps.title: Qwen Image Edit Plus 12 Steps
Qwen Image Edit Plus 12 Steps.description: This is fast Qwen Image Edit Plus 2509 (like FLUX Kontext) with 12 steps. It supports up to 3 input images and this is an amazing model. We are using Qwen-Image-Lightning-8steps-V2.0 and will udate it when a newer better LoRA arrives.

Qwen Image Edit Plus 50 Steps.author: local
Qwen Image Edit Plus 50 Steps.title: Qwen Image Edit Plus 50 Steps
Qwen Image Edit Plus 50 Steps.description: This is fast Qwen Image Edit Plus 2509 (like FLUX Kontext) with 50 steps. It is using CFG 1.5 however its quality is still not matching demo examples. I am still in research. I think ComfyUI implementation is still broken. You can reduce steps count to 20.

Qwen Image Edit Plus UHD Realism - 4+4 S.author: local
Qwen Image Edit Plus UHD Realism - 4+4 S.title: Qwen Image Edit Plus UHD Realism - 4+4 Steps
Qwen Image Edit Plus UHD Realism - 4+4 S.description: This is Qwen Image Edit Plus 2656x2656 pixel realism preset and it makes extremely high quality realistic images. This preset is made for training your subject on Qwen Image Edit Plus 2509 model with pure black control images. It yields excellent realism and quality and prompt following. The very best so far.

Qwen Image Realism Fast.author: local
Qwen Image Realism Fast.title: Qwen Image Realism Fast
Qwen Image Realism Fast.description: This is Qwen image highest realism. This one doesn't use CFG thus it is 2x faster and more realistic output. It is a little bit lesser prompt following and at some things lower quality.

Qwen Image UHD High Realism 4+4 Steps.author: local
Qwen Image UHD High Realism 4+4 Steps.title: Qwen Image UHD High Realism 4+4 Steps
Qwen Image UHD High Realism 4+4 Steps.description: This is Qwen Image 2656x2656 pixel realism preset and it makes extremely high-quality realistic images on trained Qwen Image models like self-trained Qwen Image LoRA or Qwen Image Fine Tuned model. This is 4 steps base + 4 steps upscale config. This significantly increases the realism with a little bit loss of fantastic prompts capability. You can increase the used realism LoRA strength to 0.8 for even further realism. 0.6 is working really good and balanced.

Qwen Image UHD Realism Tier - 4+4 Steps.author: local
Qwen Image UHD Realism Tier - 4+4 Steps.title: Qwen Image UHD Realism Tier - 4+4 Steps
Qwen Image UHD Realism Tier - 4+4 Steps.description: This is Qwen Image 2656x2656 pixel realism preset and it makes extremely high quality realistic images on trained Qwen Image models like self trained Qwen Image LoRA or Qwen Image Fine Tuned model. This is 4 steps base + 4 steps upscale config. This is preset is excellent for very hard and complex prompts rather than like real life photo prompts. Also you can reduce LoRA weight / strenght / scale to 0.7 for more realism.

Qwen Image UHD UlRealism 4+4 Steps.author: local
Qwen Image UHD UlRealism 4+4 Steps.title: Qwen Image UHD UlRealism 4+4 Steps
Qwen Image UHD UlRealism 4+4 Steps.description: This is Qwen Image 2656x2656 pixel realism preset and it makes extremely high-quality realistic images on trained Qwen Image models like self-trained Qwen Image LoRA or Qwen Image Fine Tuned model. This is 4 steps base + 4 steps upscale config. This ultra increases realism but you will lose all flexibility of the model. It will be only able to generate images that exists in real life. You can increase the used realism LoRA strength to 0.8 for even further realism.

Qwen Images Stylized UHD Tier 1.author: local
Qwen Images Stylized UHD Tier 1.title: Qwen Images Stylized UHD Tier 1
Qwen Images Stylized UHD Tier 1.description: This is a preset to generate stylized UHD images with your Qwen trained models whether it is Qwen Image base or Qwen Image Edit Plus 2509 model. This preset does 12 steps base and 10 steps upscale into 2656x2656 pixels. This is slower than Tier 2 but higher quality.

Qwen Images Stylized UHD Tier 2.author: local
Qwen Images Stylized UHD Tier 2.title: Qwen Images Stylized UHD Tier 2
Qwen Images Stylized UHD Tier 2.description: This is a preset to generate stylized UHD images with your Qwen trained models whether it is Qwen Image base or Qwen Image Edit Plus 2509 model. This preset does 12 steps base and 4 steps upscale into 2656x2656 pixels.

SDXL Generation With Realism Negative.description: SDXL Models Best Settings With Realism Negative Prompt

Upscale Images 2X.author: local
Upscale Images 2X.title: Upscale Images 2X
Upscale Images 2X.description: This is a realism oriented extremely high quality latent 2x upscale workflow that is tested with SD 1.5, SDXL, SD 3.5, FLUX, Qwen Image, Wan 2.1, Wan 2.2 image generation workflows and presets we have. For this to work, set everything with direct apply or reuse parameters, and then do direct apply this preset. E.g. 1024x1024 base resolution will become 2048x2048. It is fully dynamic and uses whatever you use as base.
